# EditorConfigлҠ” лӢӨм–‘н•ң м—җл””н„°мҷҖ IDEм—җм„ң мқјкҙҖлҗң мҪ”л”© мҠӨнғҖмқјмқ„ мң м§Җн•ҳлҸ„лЎқ лҸ„мҷҖмӨҚлӢҲлӢӨ
# editorconfig.org

root = true

[*]
charset = utf-8
end_of_line = lf
indent_size = 4
indent_style = space
insert_final_newline = true
trim_trailing_whitespace = true
max_line_length = 120

[*.{kt,kts}]
# Kotlin нҠ№нҷ” м„Өм •
indent_size = 4
indent_style = space
continuation_indent_size = 4
insert_final_newline = true
max_line_length = 120

[*.{java}]
# Java м„Өм • (н•„мҡ”н•ң кІҪмҡ°)
indent_size = 4
indent_style = space
continuation_indent_size = 8

[*.{xml}]
# XML м„Өм •
indent_size = 4
indent_style = space
continuation_indent_size = 4

[*.{json,yml,yaml}]
# JSON/YAML м„Өм •
indent_size = 2
indent_style = space

[*.md]
# Markdown м„Өм •
trim_trailing_whitespace = false
max_line_length = off

[gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.properties]
# Gradle wrapper мҶҚм„ұмқҖ мҲҳм •н•ҳм§Җ м•ҠмқҢ
indent_size = unset
indent_style = unset